race.description: Nzb Ready To Run 12 & 13 Nov Hcp (C1)
race.comment: OCEAN CHILL (5) justified the good support on debut when leading throughout as fav with a comfortable victory over 1400m at Scone. Finds a fairly average C1 and maps to get her chance again. SANTATIME (2) consistent gelding who will relish Farr's 2kg claim after resuming with a fast finishing second over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Should get the right tempo and can race a little closer to the speed. ROSE WATER (7) well supported at her first run back when a gritty on pace second over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Drops in weight and regular rider hops back aboard. Value prospect. TULIPWOOD (6) is resuming today but will be fitter for a recent trial, looks a place chance fresh
